section.section:
The Fund shall be used to pay for:
carrying out Article 47 of the Maryland Declaration of Rights;
carrying out the guidelines for the treatment and assistance for victims and witnesses of crimes and delinquent acts provided in §§ 11-1002 and 11-1003 of this title;
carrying out any laws enacted to benefit victims and witnesses of crimes and delinquent acts; and
supporting child advocacy centers established under § 11-923(h) of this subtitle.
